RadioButtonBar control for setting the value of c
 to Blue, Green or Blue.\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9857351436027718`*^9, 
  3.9857351618418503`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"196dab80-f42a-1241-9afe-\
