Cell["\<\
Exercise2
Use DynamicModule to modify this program to localize the dynamic variable:\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.985735199951235*^9},ExpressionUUID->"27e7d5f2-eb5c-a247-b4aa-\
45e27d58da39"],

