Cell["\<\
Exercise1
Change this Manipulate program to use a Locator control rather than a pair of \
sliders for controlling the location of a circle in a graphic:\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.985742585119993*^9},ExpressionUUID->"447fd191-156d-be4d-9050-\
5cf196548cbc"],

