aac7e5809cc8"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Exercise1
Add a frame and frame labels x and y for the horizontal and vertical scales \
in this plot, with all of the labels (including tick labels) given in 16 \
point font:\
\>", "Subsection",
